    "name": "Scorchie Adventures",
    "steam_appid": 3176520,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/6432943a8c5d029eff79c951bef2f2b0.avif?t=1771432102\" width=1352 height=530 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>A classic tight platformer for casual and hardcore players alike!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help <strong>Scorchie</strong>, a friendly and hyperactive will-o'-wisp, to save his friends against a mysterious and perverse sludge while venturing out into a vast and diverse world in this tight platformer game friendly to both casual and hardcore players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Two different game modes, tons of collectables and easy-to-learn mechanics!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy-to-learn and hard-to-master mechanics: <strong>walk, jump and dash</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic mode</strong>: the classic experience! A challenging mode created for players that are used to platformer games!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Casual mode:</strong> Recommended for players unused to platformer games and children! Get access to features like double jump, dash assist, double dash and much more! Customize your gameplay to your liking!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Berries and Crystals</strong>: Those collectables are everywhere! Gotta collect'em all!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/af99db9b0291e42dbddd07713e349cc3.poster.avif?t=1771432102\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/af99db9b0291e42dbddd07713e349cc3.webm?t=1771432102\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/af99db9b0291e42dbddd07713e349cc3.mp4?t=1771432102\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/e101f8e0b7c8b7d95ad1ac481b7f8468.avif?t=1771432102\" width=150 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Make Uncle Coal proud!</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Venture into <strong>5 exotic worlds</strong> while saving your friends!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Power Ups</strong> that totally change the gameplay!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massive variety of <strong>platforming challenges</strong>!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charismatic characters and enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>...Is that... A sludge tsunami?!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be aware of the purple sludge monsters, they bite!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A massive variety of enemies and obstacles!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/247ac80d92896ef776d8057bde6a7223.apng?t=1771432102\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/247ac80d92896ef776d8057bde6a7223.poster.avif?t=1771432102\" class=\"bb_img\" width=165 height=135 /></picture></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/492103cc56e4336b4c9268ad750ad3af.apng?t=1771432102\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176520/extras/492103cc56e4336b4c9268ad750ad3af.poster.avif?t=1771432102\" class=\"bb_img\" width=144 height=168 /></picture></span></p></li></ul>",
